7️⃣ Best Practices

Use star schema → easier DAX and performance

Avoid calculated columns if you can use measures

Limit visuals → avoid performance issues

Name measures & columns clearly

Use data types correctly

Document your data lineage & sources

Enable Row-Level Security (RLS) if needed

